/* * 잔액이 있는 대출자들의 리스트 * 대출금 잔액장 LEND_KND_CD :1 대출 2: 임차대출 */ SELECT A.MOUI_NO AS MOUI_NO,
    CASE B.MOUI_DVSN_CD WHEN '0' THEN NVL(C.USER_NM,'') ELSE NVL(B.OGNZ_NM,'') END AS MOUI_DVSN_CD,
    A.LEND_BL AS LEND_BL
FROM TBCSPNBK202M A , TBCSPNBK001M B , TBDCMACM001M C WHERE A.MOUI_NO = B.MOUI_NO AND B.TRGT_NOP_ENO (+)= C.TRGT_NOP_ENO AND A.LEND_BL > 0 AND B.SCS_YN = 'N' AND A.LEND_KND_CD = #LEND_KND_CD# ORDER BY A.MOUI_NO